sect1.sect2:
  Main Screen (User's View)
&dash-main-screen;


   If you are logged in as user, the main screen only shows the
   Project tab.  It shows details for the projects (or
    tenants) that you are a member of.

  &dash-project-tab;

Pausing, Suspending, Rebooting or Terminating Instances &inst-terminate;
&inst-terminate-warn;
Log in to &cloud; ‐.
If you are a member of multiple projects, select a Project from the drop-down list at the top of the tab.
Click the Instances & Volumes category.
Select the instance which to put out of the running state. From the Actions drop-down list, select the respective action.
